sns.set(font_scale=2)
cat_cols = ["Color", "Item Purchased", "Location"]
palettes = ["pastel", "flare", "husl"]
fig, axes = plt.subplots(nrows=3, ncols=1, figsize=(50, 20))
axes = axes.flatten()
for i, column in enumerate(cat_cols):
    sns.countplot(x=column, data=df_new, ax=axes[i])
    axes[i].set_title(f'Countplot of {column}')
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
